Summary(pl):	Email::MIME::Encodings - jednolity interfejs do kodowania i dekodowania MIME
Name:		perl-Email-MIME-Encodings
Version:	1.0
Release:	1
# same as perl
License:	GPL/Artistic
Group:		Development/Languages/Perl
